CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. A1, reads: "Oops! - Pretty Sarah Burney, 767 Anaheim St., almost slips from her lofty perch atop the diving board of a local swimming pool, but balances neatly for the photographer. The pretty and shapely lass lists dancing and swimming as her hobbies and plans to enter school next February. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Sarah Burney wearing light colored one piece strapless bathing suit with dark pattern along bust line, standing on edge of diving board over swimming pool, at Ammon Recreation Center
